{"title":"All-New Scott Patron eRIDE eMTB Evolves Big Mountain Integration in Carbon or Alloy","link":"https://bikerumor.com/all-new-scott-patron-eride-emtb-evolves-big-mountain-integration-in-carbon-or-alloy/","date":1733410800000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Richard-Bord_riding-black-rocks-1536x1024.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"(Photo by Richard Bord/Scott)\" /></p>\n<p>The all-new Scott Patron eRIDE is truly the next level of the Swiss bike makers goal to smooth out their mountain bikes’ lines and hide all of the suspension &amp; ebike tech inside the frame, protected from the element. Dialing back its travel a bit to 150mm out back, Scott gives the new Patron an all-new 4-bar suspension design and more capable &amp; adjustable geometry, while at the same time tucking the rear shock and the latest Bosch Performace CX motor and a 800Wh battery entirely inside both carbon and aluminum frame versions.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>All-New Scott Patron eRIDE eMTB</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Richard-Bord_angled-bike-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Richard-Bord_angled-bike-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2025 Scott Patron eRIDE eMTB all mountain ebike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Richard-Bord_angled-bike-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Richard-Bord_angled-bike-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Richard-Bord_angled-bike-1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Richard-Bord_angled-bike-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Richard-Bord_angled-bike-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos by Richard Bord &amp; Daniel Geiger/Scott)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Scott’s all-mountain to enduro Patron eRIDE eMTB was already one of the most integrated when it tucked its vertically-oriented motor &amp; shock under special covers in the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/scott-patron-eride-long-travel-emtb-boasts-next-level-integration-with-hidden-shock/\" target=\"_blank\">previous generation</a>. But this new generation takes a big step futher. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_new-Bosch-Performance-CX-motor-with-cover-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_new-Bosch-Performance-CX-motor-with-cover-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2025 Scott Patron eRIDE eMTB all mountain ebike, new Bosch Performance CX motor with moto-inspired cover\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_new-Bosch-Performance-CX-motor-with-cover-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_new-Bosch-Performance-CX-motor-with-cover-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_new-Bosch-Performance-CX-motor-with-cover-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_new-Bosch-Performance-CX-motor-with-cover-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_new-Bosch-Performance-CX-motor-with-cover-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_new-Bosch-Performance-CX-motor-with-cover-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_new-Bosch-Performance-CX-motor-with-cover-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now the latest, smoother Bosch <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/boschs-new-performance-cx-ebike-motor-is-not-more-powerful-but-is-better-and-lighter/\" target=\"_blank\">Performace CX motor</a> goes back to a horizontal orientation under a new motocross-inspired cover.. Scott calls it their “<em>most impact-resistant component ever</em>“. They designed it first to protect the motor. But thanks to rubber contact against the motor itself, it also damps motor noise for quieter eMTB riding.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And then, the new 800Wh PowerTube battery gets tucked inside the oversized downtube, behind a tool-free but secure protective easy-access door.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_transparent-frame-showing-shock-inside-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2400\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_transparent-frame-showing-shock-inside-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2025 Scott Patron eRIDE eMTB all mountain ebike, translucent X-ray frame\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_transparent-frame-showing-shock-inside-jpg.webp 2400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_transparent-frame-showing-shock-inside-297x186.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_transparent-frame-showing-shock-inside-1536x960.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_transparent-frame-showing-shock-inside-120x75.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_transparent-frame-showing-shock-inside-768x480.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_transparent-frame-showing-shock-inside-2048x1280.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus, the new Patron eRide eMTB gets the same upside-down shock hidden from mud inside the downtube like all the latest <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=scott+mountain+bike\" target=\"_blank\">Scott Bold-inspired mountain bikes</a>. Only this time, there’s a removable cover at the front of the seattube for easier shock access, taking cues from the previous Patron. And there are also partial covers for the builds with piggy-back shocks.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_shock-door-open-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_shock-door-open-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2025 Scott Patron eRIDE eMTB all mountain ebike, shock door cover open\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_shock-door-open-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_shock-door-open-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_shock-door-open-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_shock-door-open-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_shock-door-open-768x461.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Adjustable, adaptable geometry</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Richard-Bord_riding-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Richard-Bord_riding-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2025 Scott Patron eRIDE eMTB all mountain ebike, riding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Richard-Bord_riding-jpg.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Richard-Bord_riding-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Richard-Bord_riding-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Richard-Bord_riding-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Richard-Bord_riding-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Richard-Bord_riding-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Richard-Bord_riding-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Shifting the new Patron eRide into a more versatile eMTB, Scott starts off with a slightly steeper head angle (now 65.8° vs. 65° in the previous generation) and about 1cm longer Reacg. But that’s really just to give them more flexibility to play around. So then, the Super Trail ST versions can get a longer travel fork pushing it to a 64.9° head angle, and effectively bringing Reach back to what it was before. But that’s all in the standard -0.6° headset starting position.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_geometry-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2100\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_geometry-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2025 Scott Patron eRIDE eMTB all mountain ebike, adjustable geometry\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_geometry-jpg.webp 2100w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_geometry-297x283.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_geometry-1536x1463.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_geometry-120x114.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_geometry-768x731.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_geometry-2048x1950.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes, thanks to a +/-0.6° adjustable headset, buyers can easily further tweak how the want the new ebike to handle riding the steepest terrain. (New Patrons all also come with the 0° no-offset headset cups if they’d prefer an in-between position.)</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Carbon or Aluminum, plus some Carbon/Alloy combinations</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_carbon-or-alloy-scaled.webp\"><img width=\"2560\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_carbon-or-alloy-scaled.webp\" alt=\"2025 Scott Patron eRIDE eMTB all mountain ebike, in carbon or aluminum alloy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_carbon-or-alloy-scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_carbon-or-alloy-297x124.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_carbon-or-alloy-1536x640.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_carbon-or-alloy-120x50.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_carbon-or-alloy-768x320.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_carbon-or-alloy-2048x853.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Of course, integration is all the rage, and Scott is all about hiding everything inside. But it’s also pretty interesting that they managed to tuck shock, motor &amp; battery seamlessly inside the frame – both with carbon and alloy mainframes. Balancing weight savings and cost, Scott also has a carbon and aluminum version of the rear triangle as well. Although, only the more aggressive riding ST version gets the option of carbon seat &amp; chainstays.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech details</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_in-full-carbon-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2400\" height=\"1350\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_in-full-carbon-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2025 Scott Patron eRIDE eMTB all mountain ebike, in carbon\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_in-full-carbon-jpg.webp 2400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_in-full-carbon-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_in-full-carbon-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_in-full-carbon-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_in-full-carbon-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_in-full-carbon-2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_in-full-carbon-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a><figcaption>full carbon</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>150mm Virtual 4 Link 4-bar rear travel with upside-down shocks hidden in the seattube behind an access door</li>\n\n\n\n<li>external Sag indicator for easy suspension setup and to keep track of how you use the rear travel </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Bosch Performance CX ebike motor protected by impact-resistant moto cover</li>\n\n\n\n<li>simple toptube-mounted Bosch controller and LED display, plus thumb remote</li>\n\n\n\n<li>800Wh PowerTube internal battery, plus option to run a 250Wh PowerMore external tange extender battery </li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_toptube-cockpit-view-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_toptube-cockpit-view-1536x1536.webp\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_toptube-cockpit-view-1536x1536.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_toptube-cockpit-view-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_toptube-cockpit-view-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_toptube-cockpit-view-768x768.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_toptube-cockpit-view-jpg.webp 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_SAGometer-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_SAGometer-1536x1536.webp\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_SAGometer-1536x1536.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_SAGometer-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_SAGometer-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_SAGometer-768x768.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_SAGometer-jpg.webp 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_rear-angled-detail-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1229\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_rear-angled-detail-1536x1229.webp\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_rear-angled-detail-1536x1229.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_rear-angled-detail-297x238.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_rear-angled-detail-120x96.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_rear-angled-detail-768x614.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_rear-angled-detail-jpg.webp 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>integrated Syncros taillights on both seatstays</li>\n\n\n\n<li>angle adjust headset</li>\n\n\n\n<li>UDH universal derailleur compatibility</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Boost 12x148mm thru-axle with 55mm chainline</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Bosch Pro ABS brakes on the 2 top-tier models</li>\n\n\n\n<li>29 x 2.6″ tire clearance</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_in-alloy-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"2400\" height=\"1350\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_in-alloy-jpg.webp\" alt=\"2025 Scott Patron eRIDE eMTB all mountain ebike, in aluminum alloy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_in-alloy-jpg.webp 2400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_in-alloy-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_in-alloy-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_in-alloy-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_in-alloy-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_in-alloy-2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_in-alloy-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a><figcaption>all-alloy</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>2025 Scott Patron eRIDE eMTB – Pricing, options &amp; availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_Patron-900-angled-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_Patron-900-angled-1536x1536.webp\" alt=\"2025 Scott Patron eRIDE eMTB all mountain ebike, standard all-rounder\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_Patron-900-angled-1536x1536.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_Patron-900-angled-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_Patron-900-angled-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_Patron-900-angled-768x768.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_Patron-900-angled-jpg.webp 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_Patron-900-ST-Tuned-angled-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_Patron-900-ST-Tuned-angled-1536x1536.webp\" alt=\"2025 Scott Patron eRIDE eMTB all mountain ebike, ST Super Trail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_Patron-900-ST-Tuned-angled-1536x1536.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_Patron-900-ST-Tuned-angled-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_Patron-900-ST-Tuned-angled-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_Patron-900-ST-Tuned-angled-768x768.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/MY25-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_photo-by-Daniel-Geiger_Patron-900-ST-Tuned-angled-jpg.webp 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are looking for a capable big mountain ebike, Scott has <a href=\"https://www.scott-sports.com/global/en/patron\" target=\"_blank\">plenty of options</a> with their all-new Patron eMTB. Two styles based on the same main frames, and 6 models in all. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The standard “do-it-all” Scott Patron eRide eMTB sticks with matching 150mm travel front &amp; rear and versatile Maxxis trail tires. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Or the super trail Patron eRide ST ratchets that up to 170mm of fork travel to the 150mm rear travel, and gives them extra grip of Schwalbe’s latest Radial mountain bike tire tech and extra sticky rubber. Built for “aggressive technical trails and handling bigger impacts.”</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-920-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"922\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-920-1536x922.webp\" alt=\"2025 Scott Patron eRIDE eMTB all mountain ebike, 920\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-920-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-920-297x178.webp 29