0-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-900-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-900-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-900-768x461.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-900-jpg.webp 2000w\" /></a><figcaption>Patron eRIDE 900</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Pricing starts at 6000€ for the fully alloy 25.8kg Patron eRide 920, 7700€ for the carbon front/alloy rear 24.3kg Patron eRide 910, and 8800€ for the 24.4kg Patron eRide 900 also with a carbon/alloy frameset.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-ST-910-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"922\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-ST-910-1536x922.webp\" alt=\"2025 Scott Patron eRIDE eMTB all mountain ebike, ST 910\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-ST-910-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-ST-910-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-ST-910-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-ST-910-768x461.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-ST-910-jpg.webp 2000w\" /></a><figcaption>Patron eRIDE ST 910</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-ST-900-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"922\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-ST-900-1536x922.webp\" alt=\"2025 Scott Patron eRIDE eMTB all mountain ebike, ST 900\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-ST-900-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-ST-900-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-ST-900-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-ST-900-768x461.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-ST-900-jpg.webp 2000w\" /></a><figcaption>Patron eRIDE ST 900</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-ST-900-TUNED-jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"922\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-ST-900-TUNED-1536x922.webp\" alt=\"2025 Scott Patron eRIDE eMTB all mountain ebike, ST 900 Tuned\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-ST-900-TUNED-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-ST-900-TUNED-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-ST-900-TUNED-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2025-Scott-Patron-eRIDE-eMTB-all-mountain-ebike_PATRON-ST-900-TUNED-768x461.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-c